  ¡§Goa2 ai3 kap lin2 tam5-oe7, che7 teh si7 chin ho2.¡¨ Kam-tok na2 kong2 na2 che7 loh8 ti7 chioh8-thau5 teng2. 
  ¡§Li2 un2-tang3 tong5-cheng5 goan2 chit-khoan2 lang5, goan2 si7 kiaN5 te7-gek8 lou7 e5 lang5, te7-gek8 ia7 si7 khiam3 goan2 chit-khoan2 pi2 Mou5-kui2 khah ho2 tam7-poh8 e5 lang5 lai5 chhoa7 lou7, ha3! ha3!¡¨ hit-e5 khia7 teh e5 an2-ni kong2. 
  ¡§Goa2 oe7-thang pang-chan7 lin2 sim2-mih8 bo5?¡¨ Kam-tok chin un-jiu5 an2-ni kong2. 
  Che7 teh hit-e5, kim-kim siong3 kam-tok chiu7 khui-chhui3 kong2: ¡§Sian-siN, li2 oe7 jin7 tit goa2 mah?¡¨ 
  ¡§Boe7, in-ui7 hoe2 bo5 chin kng.¡¨ Kam-tok in3. 
  ¡§An2-ni chiu7 oe7 khoaN3 chheng-chho2 la3!¡¨ Che7 teh hit-e5 chiu7 peh khi2-lai5, thng3 bo7-a2, khia7-oa2 kam-tok e5 bin7-cheng5. Chit-e5 lang5 e5 thau5-mng5 chin ou, chi2-u7 thau5-khak-sim e5 sou2-chai7 u7 chit8 jiah peh8-peh8. Kam-tok khoaN3-tioh8 hit-jiah chiu7 siuN7 tioh8 15 ni5 cheng5 e5 su7. 
  ¡§He si7 15 ni5 cheng5 e5 su7 la3! Li2 oe7 ki3-tit chit8 e5 lang5 khi3 ka7 li2 kong2 i e5 bou2-kiaN2 long2 ti7 Niu2-iok8 hoe2-sio chhu3 e5 si5 sio si2 e5 su7 mah?¡¨ 
  ¡§Si7 la3! Si7 la3! goa2 oe7 ki3-tit¡¨. Kam-tok thim3-thau5, hit-e5 khia7 teh e5 tang5-phoaN7 ia7 chu3-sin5 teh thiaN. 
  ¡§Hit am3 li2 lau5 goa2 tiam3 li2 hia, keh jit8 koh ui7 goa2 chhoe7 thau5-lou7, chhoe7 tioh8 kou3 chhng-khou3 e5 chit, goa2 ia7 kap li2 iok beh kim3-chiu2.¡¨ 
  ¡§Si7 la3! Li2 kaN2 u7 siu2 iok hoN3!¡¨ 
  Hit-e5 lang5 thou2 chit8 e7 toa7-khui3, koh chhun chhiu2 toa7-lat8 cheng piah, chhiu2 soa3 lau5-huih. 
  ¡§Bo5 ah! Thai2 u7 siu2 le3! Bo5 chit8 le2-pai3 chiu7 koh lim, hian7-chai7 ia7 si7. Chong2-si7 li2 e5 ki5-to2 goa2 eng2-oan2 boe7-oe7 boe7-ki3-tit. Goa2 hit cha2-khi2 hou7 lin2 chhiaN2 e5 si5, li2 u7 ki5-to2, hit-e5 cheng5-heng5 khek ti7 goa2 e5 sim-lai7. Goa2 e5 lau7-bo2 ti7 goa2 soe3-han3 e5 si5 ia7 tak8 am3 ui7 goa2 ki5-to2, u7 chit8 am3 lau7-bo2 teh ki5-to2, lau7-pe7 chiah8 chiu2 tng2-lai5 chiu7 that-to2 lau7-bo2. Hit cha2-khi2 li2 e5 ki5-to2 tu2-tu2 chhin-chhiuN7 lau7-bo2 e5 ki5-to2. Goa2 hit jit8 khi3 chhoe7 li2 e5 si5 tu2 chhin-chhiuN7 chui3-han3, chong2-si7 li2 ia7 siu-liu5 goa2. Ah! goa2 sit8-chai7 tui3-put-chu7 li2. Goa2 i2-au7 e5 seng-oah8 long2 si7 ti7 chiu2-ka chhut-jip8, chong2-si7 li2 e5 ki5-to2 siong5-siong5 chhin-chhiuN7 chiam chhak8 goa2 e5 sim. Goa2 e5 thau5-lou7 i2-keng sit-loh8, ia7 bat lo5-hoan5 keng2-chhat. Ah! Sian-siN ah, goa2 bo5 beh siong-hai7 li2, li2 thang tng2-khi3 la3!¡¨ 
  Kam-tok long2 bo5 tin2-tang7, m7 chai to2-ui7 e5 si5-cheng kong3 chit8 tiam2, hit-e5 lang5 ti3 bo7-a2 koh che7 loh8-lai5. Ah! Kam-tok e5 sim kam2-khai3 moa2-moa2. 
  ¡§Li2 bo5 thau5-lou7 i2-keng joa7-ku2 lah?¡¨ Kam-tok mng7 i, khia7 teh hit-e5 in3 kong2: 
  ¡§PoaN3-ni5 lai5, tu5-liau2 chhiuN2-kiap i2-goa7 si7 bo5 cho3 sim2-mih8 kang la3! Sian-siN ah! ChhiuN2-kiap si7 chin bo5 sim-sek ne3! U7 si5 chhin-chhiuN7 e7-am3 tit bo5 poaN3-chiam!¡¨ 
  ¡§Si7 la3! Na7-si7 an2-ni, goa2 na7 the3 lin2 chhoe7 u7 thau5-lou7, lin2 hoaN-hi2 pan7 chit-e5 kang mah?¡¨ 
  ¡§Sian-siN ah bo5 chhai2-kang la3! Goa2 i2-keng hoe2-kai2 kui2-na7 pai2, chong2-si7 bo5 pan7-hoat, poah ti7 Mou5-kui2 e5 lo5-bang7 la3! siuN7 ban7 la3! Bo5 thang koh ke2-piN3 e5 ng3-bang7 la3!¡¨ Che7 ti7 chioh8-teng2 hit-e5 an2-ni in3. 
  ¡§Bo5 ah! m7-thang an2-ni kong2¡¨. Kam-tok an2-ni kong2, chong2-si7 ti7 i e5 sim boe7 bat seN-khi2 chiah-nih jiat8-chhiat ai3 kiu3 lang5 leng5-hun5 e5 sim. ¡§Oh! Chu2 ah! chiong chit nng7 e5 leng5-hun5 hou7 goa2, Chu2 ah! ui7 Li2 e5 mia5 e5 ian5-kou3, chin2-kiu3 chit nng7 e5 lang5,¡¨ i put-toan7 ti7 i e5 sim-te2 teh kiu5. 
  ¡§Lin2 m7-thang an2-ni siuN7, Siong7-te3 m7 chai beh eng7 lin2 kau3 chaiN2-iuN7, lin2 si7 Siong7-te3 e5 po2-poe3¡¨. Kam-tok hoan2-hok an2-ni kong2. Chit si5 kam-tok pun2 sou2 u7 chin ho2 e5 ki3-ek-lek8 hou7 i siuN7 tioh8 15 ni5 cheng5 khi3 chhoe7 i chit-e5 lang5 e5 mia5. 
  ¡§Pa-su kun!¡¨ Kam-tok eng7 moa2 u7 thiaN3-cheng5 e5 gu2-khi3 kio3 i e5 mia5 hou7 i tioh8 toa7-kiaN. 
  ¡§Pa-su kun kap li2 e5 peng5-iu2 lin2 nng7-lang5 kim-am3 na7 kheng2 kau3 goa2 e5 chhu3, goa2 it-teng7 ui7 lin2 chhoe7 cheng3-tong e5 thau5-lou7. Lin2 na7 siuN7 se3-kan iau2 u7 thiaN3 e5 chun5-chai7, chhiaN2 lin2 siong-sin3 goa2 si7 thiaN3 lin2 e5. Sit8-chai7 goa2 u7 thiaN3 lin2, goa2 ti7 thiaN3 goa2 ui7 goa2 si2 e5 Chu2 Ia5-sou e5 bin7-cheng5, goa2 boe7 thang khoaN3 lin2 loh8 te7-gek8. Lai5, saN-kap lai5-khi3, lai5 sin chhut-hoat, e7-am3 e5 su7 lan2 i2-goa7 bo5 lang5 chai, Siong7-te3 ia7 hoaN-hi2 sia3-bian2 lin2. KiN3-na7 kiu5 I sia3-bian2, I boe7 oe7 bo5 sia3-bian2. Lai5, lan2 saN lang5 saN-kap lai5 ki5-to2. Ki-tok lai5 se3-kan si7 ui7-tioh8 beh chin2-kiu3 choe7-jin5. Ah! Chu2 ah! Kiu3 chit nng7 tiau5 leng5-hun5.¡¨ 
  Kam-tok jiat8-liat8 ai3 kiu3 in e5 sim, ki5-to2 i2-goa7 bo5 oe7 thang kong2-chhut. Kam-tok khai-si2 ki5-to2 bo5 ku2, Pa-su chiu7 chhiu2 am-bin7, na2 hau2 na2 kui7 loh8-khi3. Ah! Pa-su e5 lau7-bo2 hian7-kim ti7 ta2-loh8 teh ui7 i e5 kiaN2-ji5 ki5-to2 ah? I e5 ki5-to2 ia7 un2-tang3 kap kam-tok e5 ki5-to2 saN tang5-sim. I2-cheng5 m7-bat kam-tok hit-e5 khi2-thau5 khia7 ti7 chhiuN5-a2-piN e5 tang5-phoaN7, au7-lai5 ia7 siu7 kam-tok e5 ki5-to2 sou2 kam2-tong7. Ah! ki5-biau7 ah! Seng3 Sin5 e5 khui3-lat8! Cha2 si5 ti7 Tai7-ma2-sek e5 lou7-chiuN7 taN2-to2 So3-lo5 e5 Seng3 Sin5, i2-kip8 tng Ma2 bok8-su koat-teng7 beh kun-te3 Ia5-sou e5 si5, kang3-loh8 ti7 Te7-it kau3-hoe7 kap Na2-sat-lek8 kau3-hoe7 e5 Seng3 Sin5, chit-si5 ia7 kang3-lim5 ti7 Chi-ka-ko kek8 ou-am3 e5 sou2-chai7, ti7 bo5 liong5-sim, bo5 u7 Siong7-te3 chun5-chai7 e5 nng7 e5 kiong5-to7 e5 sin-chiuN7, lian5 in pun2-sin ia7 tioh8-kiaN. 
  Kam-tok ki5-to2 liau2, Pa-su iau2 teh lau5 bak8-sai2, the ti7 chhiuN5-a2. Leng7-goa7 hit-e5 ia7 in-ui7 hoe2-kai2 chhiong-moa2 hoaN-hi2, na7 si7 iau2-ku2 u7 kian3-siau3 e5 khoan2-sit. 
  ¡§Lai5, Siong7-te3 si7 lin5-bin2 e5 Siong7-te3, e7-am3 lin2 lai5 tiam3 sit8-bin5-koan2, thau5-lou7 goa2 oe7 siat-hoat.¡¨ 
  Nng7-lang5 chiu7 toe3 kam-tok kiaN5, kau3 sit8-bin5-koan2 e5 si5 i2-keng si7 2 tiam2. Kam-tok chhoa7 in kau3 chit8 keng pang5-keng hioh-khun3, kam-tok beh li7-khui pang5-keng e5 si5 i e5 bin7 sui-jian5 in-ui7 chiah ku2 e5 lo5-tong7 ke chin san2, iau2-ku2 sit8-chai7 u7 hoat-chhut Siong7-te3 e5 eng5-kng. 
  Keh cha2-khi2 kam-tok beh khi3 chhoe7 in, sim iau2 lun2-lun2, chong2-si7 cha-me5 e5 kam2-khai3 iau2 ti7 i e5 sim, chiu7 chiau3 iok ui7 in chhoe7 thau5-lou7. Chiu7 si7 hou7 Pa-su cho3 sit8-bin5-koan2 e5 kang-iah8, i e5 tang5-phoaN7 cho3 hu7-kin7 be2-chhia-tiam3 e5 chhia-hu, an2-ni nng7-lang5 chiu7 beh khai-si2 sin e5 seng-oah8 la3! 
  Hit e7-pou chit8 e5 sin-lai5 e5 kang-iah8 teh chheng-sau3 sit8-bin5-koan2 e5 mng5-khau2, hut-jian5 i theng5-chhiu2 kiah8-thau5 khoaN3 chiu-ui5, khoaN3 ah! ti7 tui3-bin7 u7 ¡§Te7-it chiu2-ka¡¨ e5 chiau-pai5, koe3-khi3 koh u7 nng7-keng, oat-kak hia ia7 u7 saN-keng. Hit si5 tu2-ho2 u7 lang5 tui3 Te7-it chiu2-ka chhut-lai5, phang-phang e5 chiu2-bi7 chheng3 kau3 Pa-su e5 phiN7-khang. Pa-su kiah8 an5 i e5 sau3-chhiu2, bian2-kiong2 ai3 boe7 ki3-tit hit-e5 chiu2 e5 chu-bi7, chong2-si7 i e5 bin7 it-tit8 lau5 chhin3-koaN7, chhiu2 phih8-phih8-chhoah, chng2-thau5-a2 ia7 tng2 sek. 
  ¡§Ah! kam-tok na7 kin2 tng2-lai5 ma7 ho2!¡¨ Tu2-chiah i u7 khoaN3-tioh8 kam-tok kap Pou3 bok8-su chhut-khi3. I ke3-siok8 koh sau3 2, 3 hun cheng, chong2-si7 i na2 sau3 na2 oa2-kun7 chiu2-ka, i thng3 bo7-a2 chhit-koaN7, bak8-chiu khoaN3 tioh8 tu5-a2 lai7 e5 chiu2, choan5-sin koh thiu-chhoah. Put-ti put-kak i i2-keng kiaN5 kau3 chiu2-ka e5 mng5-khau2. I oat8-thau5 khoaN3 chiu-ui5, chiu7 chhun-chhiu2 beh khui chiu2-tu5; tng i tu2-ho2 koaN7-tioh8 chit8 kan chiu2 beh chau2 e5 si5, khoaN3 ah! tui3 hit peng5 kak-thau5 u7 chit8 e5 toa7-han3 lang5 kiaN5 lai5, i chiu7-si7 kam-tok. 
  Kam-tok tui3 i e5 chhiu2 khiu2 tiau5, thoa i beh tng2-khi3, i put-koan2 si7 sim2-mih8 lang5, chhun chhiu2 chhut-lat8 cheng-khi3, tu2-ho2 cheng-tioh8 kam-tok e5 e7-hai5, kam-tok tioh8-siong, chong2-si7 i bo5 chhut-siaN, chi2-u7 chhut-lat8 thoa i jip8 sit8-bin5-koan2, jip8 kheh-thiaN chiu7 pang3 i che7 ti7 te7-pan2, Pa-su chit si5 chiah khui-siaN thi5-khau3, kui7-teh beh ki5-to2. 
  ¡§Pa-su, li2 tioh8 ki5-to2, pek-chhiat ki5-to2, che si7 te7-it oe7 pang-chan7 li2 e5 hong-hoat,¡¨ kam-tok e5 bin7 moa2 u7 iu-bun7 kap lin5-bin2 e5 piau2-cheng5. 
  ¡§Ah! kam-tok, chhiaN2 li2 kap goa2 saN-kap ki5-to2, kiu3 goa2 chhut te7-gek8!¡¨ Pa-su toa7-siaN au5-kio3. Kam-tok chiu7 kap i saN-kap kui7-loh8, ki5-to2 soah, Pa-su jip8 i ka-ki7 e5 pang5, hit am3 chhut-lai5 e5 si5 i2-keng chhin-chhiuN7 gin2-na2 e5 khiam-sun3. 
  Chong2-si7 tui3-bin7 e5 chiu2-ka iu5-goan5 chun5-chai7, che tui3 ti7 koat-i3 beh kiaN5 chiaN3-lou7 e5 lang5 si7 toa7 e5 iu2-hek8. SiaN2-si5 chiah oe7-thang hou7 in ti2-khong3 chiu2-bi7 e5 iu2-hek8 ah! 
  Ke3-jit8 kam-tok kap Pa bok8-su saN-kap tam5-lun7 chit-e5 su7. 
  ¡§Li2 chai-iaN2 tui3-bin7 e5 chiu2-ka si7 chi7-chui7 e5 mah?¡¨kam-tok mng7. 
  ¡§M7 chai, chong2-si7 goa2 oe7 thang tham3-thiaN. Li2 khoaN3 kiam2 u7 kho2-leng5 thang hoan2-tui3 chiu2-ka e5 chun5-chai7? In e5 se3-lek8, kap te7-poaN5 e5 kian-kou3 si7 boe7 su kau3-hoe7. Kiam2-chhai2 si7 bo5 pan7-hoat.¡¨ 
  ¡§Siong7-te3 u7 pan7-hoat, chhin-chhiuN7 hoe3-chi2 lou5-le7 che3-tou7 chit8 iuN7. Lan2 u7 pit-iau3 seng chai-iaN2 tui3-bin7 hit keng e5 sou2-iu2-chia2.¡¨ Kam-tok chin jin7-chin in3. 
  ¡§Ho2, goa2 lai5 khi3 tiau5-cha.¡¨ Pou3 bok8-su tah-eng3, nng7-jit8-au7 Pou3 bok8-su khi3 hong2-bun7 Na2-sat-lek8 kau3-hoe7 chit8 e5 hoe7-iu2, i ti7 hia siu7 toa7 hoan-geng5. 
  ¡§Kin-a2-jit8 lai5 hong2-bun7 li2 si7 ui7-tioh8 sit8-bin5-koan2 tui3-bin7 e5 chiu2-ka e5 su7. Khek-liu5-tek kun, li2 kiam2 siuN7 chiong chhu3 soe3 lang5 cho3 chiu2-ka si7 hap8-gi5 mah?¡¨ Pou3 bok8-su tit8-chiap kong2-chhut chit-e5 iau3-kiaN7 e5 si5, chit-e5 chhu3 e5 chu2-lang5, bin7 ang5, bo5 ku2 koh tng2 chheN, soa3 lau5 bak8-sai2. 
  ¡§Pou3 bok8-su, li2 kiam2 chai goa2 u7 chham-ka se7-iok mah?¡¨ 
  ¡§Si7 la3!¡¨ 
  ¡§Goa2 ui7-tioh8 hit keng chhu3 ia7 si7 chin kan-khou2 sim, he si7 Mou5-kui2 tui3 goa2 e5 toa7 iu2-hek8, in-ui7 goa2 tui3 hia e5 siu-jip8 si7 chin choe7. Goa2 tu2-chiah ia7 u7 teh siuN7 Chu2 tek-khak boe7 chiong i e5 chhu3 soe3 lang5 cho3 chiu2-ka.¡¨ Kong2 liau2 chhun-chhiu2 kap bok8-su ak-chhiu2. Nng7-lang5 kam2-khai3 moa2-moa2, bok8-su saN-si5 tng2-khi3. 
  Chit8 kou3-goeh8 au7, sit8-bin5-koan2 tui3-bin7 e5 chiu2-ka siu khi2-lai5, Khek-liu5-tek sian-siN m7 na7 koat-sim m7 soe3 lang5 cho3 chiu2-ka, koh hoaN-hi2 hou7 kam-tok kap Pa bok8-su cho3 sit8-bin5-koan2 e5 lou7-eng7. 
  Bo5 loa7-ku2 chit keng chhu3 siu7 kai2-cho7 cho3 chit8-keng ka-su7 hak8-hau7. Hui-li2 ti7 chia toa7 hoat-hui i e5 chai5-leng5, lai5 kau3-iong2 cha-bou2 gin2-na2 chu2-chiah8 e5 hoat-tou7. 
  Ah! Seng3 Sin5 e5 kang-chok ke3-siok8 teh oah8-tang7, chit-keng chiu2-ka i2-keng chiaN5-cho3 li7-ek lang5 e5 sou2-chai7 la3! 
